{"lemma":"تِبْرُ","slug":"تِبْرُ","root":"ت.ب.ر","root_slug":"ت-ب-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ت-ب-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"تِبْرُ","root":"تبر","pos":"V","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3717","n3719"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pure, unalloyed ore of gold or silver","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"الذَّهَبُ بِٱلذَّهَبِ تِبْرُهَا وَعَيْنُهَا وَٱلْفِضَّةُ بِٱلْفِضَّةِ تِبْرُهَا وَعَيْنُهَا وَٱلْبُرُّ بِٱلْبُرِّ مُدْيٌ بِمُدْيٍ وَٱلشَّعِيرُ بِٱلشَّعِيرِ مُدْيٌ بِمُدْيٍ وَٱلتَّمْرُ بِٱلتَّمْرِ مُدْيٌ بِمُدْيٍ وَٱلْمِلْحُ بِٱلْمِلْحِ مُدْيٌ بِمُدْيٍ","english":"Gold is to be weighed for in gold, raw and coined, silver in silver, raw and coined, wheat in wheat in equal measure, barley in barley in equal measure, dates in dates in equal measure, salt in salt in equal measure."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to destroy; to annihilate","examples":[{"text":"وَكُلًّا ضَرَبْنَا لَهُ ٱلْأَمْثَٰلَ وَكُلًّا تَبَّرْنَا تَتْبِيرًا","english":"For each We set forth (various) lessons, and We ultimately destroyed each."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Aramaic תְּבְרָא / ܬܷܒܪܐ (təḇrā, “fragment”), absolute state תְּבַר / ܬܒܱܪ (tḇar), from תְּבַר / ܬܒܱܪ (tḇar, “to break, to fract”), the Aramaic equivalent to Arabic ثَبَرَ (ṯabara, “to destroy”).\n\nSee the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3717","headword_ar":"تَبِرَ","root":"tbr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, T, M, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabaArN","text_ar":"تَبَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Lth, T, M;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabara","text_ar":"تَبَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, Lth, T, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perished."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, M, Msb, K.)       -A2-  See also 2."}],"source_refs":["Lth","T","M","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n3719","headword_ar":"تِبْرٌ","root":"tbr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[a coll. gen. n., of which the n. un. is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":":"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Native gold, in the form of dust"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of nuggets:"},{"kind":"text","text":"this is the sense in which the word is generally used in the present day:]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broken gold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) it is not so called unless"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the dust of its mine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broken:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IJ, M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silver, before it is wrought:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, IF, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broken,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crumbled, particles of gold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of silver, before they are wrought:"},{"kind":"text","text":"when they are wrought, they are called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahabN","text_ar":"ذَهَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiD~apN","text_ar":"فِضَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar, T, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncoined gold"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silver:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) when coined, it is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayonN","text_ar":"عَيْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb:) [properly,] the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbr","text_ar":"تبر"},{"kind":"text","text":"should not be employed save as applied to gold; but some apply it to silver also: (S:) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbr","text_ar":"تبر"},{"kind":"text","text":"of silver, as well as of gold, is mentioned in a trad.: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gold"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) universally: (M:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silver:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is extracted from the mine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of gold"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silver"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"all"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawaAhir","text_ar":"جَوَاهِر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"native ores"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before it is wrought"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and used:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawohar","text_ar":"جَوْهَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"native ore"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before it is used, of copper"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, T, Mgh, Msb) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brass"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, T, Mgh) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"iron"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, Mgh, Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jwhr","text_ar":"جوهر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"native ore"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is used, of copper and brass:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) the word is sometimes applied to other minerals than gold and silver, as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"copper"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"iron"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lead,"},{"kind":"text","text":"but generally to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gold;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and some say that its primary application is to gold, and that the other applications are later, or tropical: (TA:) also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broken pieces of glass."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, T, M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["M","IJ","Lth","T","IF","Msb","IAar","K","S","Mgh","TA","Zj"]}]}}